name: Skelevex - Cornish Copper 3 custom.
description:
The third piece in this style to be dredged up from the Cornish Coastline, this cold cast copper custom Skelevex has been lying on the sea bed for unknown years.

2.5" of solid cold cast copper resin, with a blend of painted and actual corrosion (created with a saline solution that reacts with the real copper particles).

Limited to just 1 piece, designed by Alto x DMS, produced by DMS.

Please note: Hand made, may contain small imperfections, may appear slightly different to the images due the nature of this and studio lighting/monitor settings.

Please allow up to 7 business days for shipping.

name: Skelevex - Crystal Death. Sold out!
description:
It may be blue, but it's the bomb yo!

Crystal Death Skelevex, 11 pieces of clear blue resin to commemorate the end of Breaking Bad. Measuring a solid 2.5", clear bagged as any crystal should be.

The first 6 tweakers to score will also receive a special miniature shard!

No crystal is perfect, even Heisenberg couldn't cook 100%. This batch has been tested as 96.2%, so small imperfections are to be expected*.

Please note: These are hand made resin pieces for ages 15+, may contain imperfections and appear slightly different to the above images due to monitor settings and lighting.

*No flies were present during the cook!



Please allow up to 7 working days for dispatch and up to 28 working days for delivery (depending on destination).
